{"tid":1230043,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱搭lift，有個姐姐問我:去遊行呀","createTime":"2019-06-16T05:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T06:19:57.000Z","uid":122558,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df7d530e0f9cc1ce669f7dbea96f8d2f8b6bf68a","tid":1230043,"uid":122558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:55:00.000Z","msg":"説話啱啱出門搭lift既時候，有個黑色衫姐姐過黎見到我又係黑色衫，對我笑咗笑<br />\n<br />\n之後問我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去遊行呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個仔同d朋友仔去，唔帶我，我自己去，上次我都係自己去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔緊要啦，有咁多香港陪你，加油!<br />\n<br />\n我想講香港人近年真係冷漠咗好多，住多咁耐都未試過有個三唔識七既走過黎，之後出到地鐵又係見到全黑衫，果種感覺好似返返80年代獅子山下精神，香港人守望相助，唔再冷漠，關懷他人，為同一種目標而奮鬥，真係好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876ce9f2941ce22ff6a4a8443e35a552fa5fd5ce","tid":1230043,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:19:28.000Z","msg":"食啦 一路69諗起69"},{"pid":"a1fcbbaa441044514e9af361a1a01b2078838c16","tid":1230043,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:19:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}